In [123]:
def plot_feature_importance(importance, names, model_type, top_n=4):
    # Create a DataFrame for feature importance
    feature_importance = pd.DataFrame({'Feature': names, 'Importance': importance})
    feature_importance = feature_importance.sort_values(by='Importance', ascending=False)
    
    # Select top_n features
    top_features = feature_importance.head(top_n)
    
    # Plotting
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.barplot(x=top_features['Importance'], y=top_features['Feature'])
    plt.title(f'{model_type} Feature Importance (Top {top_n})')
    plt.show()

# Feature importance from Random Forest
feature_names = X.columns
importances = rf_classifier.feature_importances_

# Plot feature importance, displaying only the top 5 features
plot_feature_importance(importances, feature_names, 'Random Forest', top_n=4)

In [125]:
# Simulasi tanpa menggunakan model machine learning
campaign_cost = 10000  # Biaya kampanye dalam dolar
conversion_rate_before = 0.02  # Konversi sebelum menggunakan model ML
revenue_per_conversion = 95  # Pendapatan per konversi dalam dolar

# Menghitung revenue dan profit sebelum menggunakan model ML
conversions_before = campaign_cost * conversion_rate_before  # Jumlah konversi
revenue_before = conversions_before * revenue_per_conversion  # Total revenue
profit_before = revenue_before - campaign_cost  # Profit

# Simulasi setelah menggunakan model machine learning
conversion_rate_after = 0.05  # Konversi setelah menggunakan model ML

# Menghitung revenue dan profit setelah menggunakan model ML
conversions_after = campaign_cost * conversion_rate_after  # Jumlah konversi
revenue_after = conversions_after * revenue_per_conversion  # Total revenue
profit_after = revenue_after - campaign_cost  # Profit

# Menampilkan hasil
results = {
    "Before ML": {
        "Conversions": conversions_before,
        "Revenue ($)": revenue_before,
        "Profit ($)": profit_before
    },
    "After ML": {
        "Conversions": conversions_after,
        "Revenue ($)": revenue_after,
        "Profit ($)": profit_after
    }
}

results
